statement.p:
Write each expression without negative exponents.


\dfrac{1}{4}xy^{-2}

a^{-3}b^{-2}

\dfrac{2a^{-1}}{{bc}^{-2}}

\dfrac{x}{y^{-2}}+\dfrac{x^{-2}}{y}

solution.p:
We use the fact that  ~a^{-n} = \dfrac{1}{a^n}, and consequently that ~\dfrac{1}{a^{-n}} = a^n.


\dfrac{x}{4y^2}

\dfrac{1}{a^{3}b^{2}}

\dfrac{2c^2}{ab}

xy^{2}+\dfrac{1}{x^2y}

